---
import ProductLayout from '@/layouts/ProductLayout.astro';
---

<ProductLayout
  title="BSupervisor — AI Audit & Safety"
  description="Watching quietly, even while you sleep."
  locale="en"
  product="BSupervisor"
  accent="#f43f5e"
  appUrl="https://supervisor.bsvibe.dev"
>
  <h1>BSupervisor</h1>
  <p class="product-tagline">Watching quietly, even while you sleep. Monitor, log, and control every action your AI agents take.</p>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Pre-execution Blocking</h3>
      <p>Check rules before agents act. Block unauthorized actions and dangerous operations proactively.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Real-time Monitoring</h3>
      <p>Detect anomalous patterns, cost spikes, and infinite loops in real time with instant alerts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Audit Logs</h3>
      <p>Complete traceability: who, when, what, and why. Auto-generate compliance reports.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Custom Rules</h3>
      <p>Define safety policies for your organization. "Require manager approval for transactions over $1,000."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Automated Compliance</h2>
  <p>Meet EU AI Act, regulatory requirements, and internal governance standards. Every agent action through BSupervisor is automatically logged — compliance without extra work.</p>

  <h2>Use Cases</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Finance</strong> — Trading agent audit trails, anomalous transaction detection</li>
    <li><strong>Healthcare</strong> — Medical AI decision tracking, misdiagnosis prevention rules</li>
    <li><strong>Enterprise</strong> — Organization-wide AI governance, SOC2 compliance reporting</li>
    <li><strong>Startups</strong> — Cost explosion prevention, basic safety policy setup</li>
  </ul>
</ProductLayout>
